<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>وقال ابن حبان في <span class="c1">"الضعفاء"</span> <span class="c2">(١/٢٤١)</span> :<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
